response.overview: Bay City Rollers Alan Longmuir, Stuart Wood and Les McKeown homecoming set at T in the Park Festival live in the King Tut's Tent at Strathallan Castle Auchterarder 9-7-2016.  Summerlove Sensation - I Only Wanna Be With You - Remember - Keep On Dancing - Be My Baby - Give a Little Love - Too Young to Rock & Roll - Please Stay - All of Me Loves All of You - I Only Want To Dance With You Tonight - Saturday Night - Have I the Right - Shang-A-Lang - Loch Lomond - Bye, Bye, Baby
response.title: Bay City Rollers: T in the Park
